For the purpose of this tutorial, you can use the `R` code below to create an itembank with polytomous items, or use `MS Excel` with [**this file**](https://osf.io/ymh3d/files/sk9hx) for an English-Dutch vocabulary test, which includes 36 dichotomous items.

