Similarly,

1.  we add a new block,
2.  rename it to 'init block'
3.  add a new **Text / Entry** question type,
4.  and enter the phrase 'Loading...' as question text.

![](images/Screenshot%202025-12-02%20at%2008.08.08.png){fig-align="center"}

